These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different games are played: bridge, whist, snooker
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, engineer, firefighter
1. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4
2. the architect is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
3. the architect is the person playing whist##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
5. the engineer is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Game   | snooker | bridge | whist |
| Job    | engineer    | firefighter | architect |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, doctor, scientist
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the doctor is in an even position##4
3. the scientist is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the doctor is the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | drawing | filmmaking | board-games |
| Job   | scientist    | doctor     | pilot        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk, fanta
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Beverage         | fanta     | soy-milk | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, polish, canadian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse
1. the polish is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the indian is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the polish is in an even position##4
4. the polish is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Nationality   | canadian | polish  | indian  |
| Sport         | biathlon  | cricket | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, aquamarine, yellow
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, dutch
1. the person who likes yellow is between the person who likes ebony and the canadian##2
2. the person who likes aquamarine is in an odd position##4
3. the dutch is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Color         | ebony   | yellow | aquamarine    |
| Nationality   | colombian | dutch     | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, iris, rose
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who growsiris is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Flower   | iris | rose | daffodil   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
House: art-deco, victorian, ranch-style
3 different pets are kept: dog, goat, turtle
1. the victorian house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
2. the art-deco house is between the owner of the turtle and the ranch-style house##2
3. the art-deco house is on the left of the victorian house##1
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| House   | ranch-style | art-deco | victorian |
| Pet           | goat         | dog         | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, almond-milk
3 different pets are kept: frog, rat, snake
1. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the rat and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | almond-milk | fanta |
| Pet    | rat    | frog | snake     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games, baking
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Hobby   | baking   | board-games  | filmmaking  |
| Sport         | tennis | lacrosse | climbing |

