3 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, monopoly
1. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | 7up    | cola      | coffee |
| Game       | billiard | monopoly | scrabble   |

