.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, ice-hockey, cycling
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
4. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Sport   | cycling | ice-hockey | swimming |
| Transport     | taxi     | scooter   | van        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, family, drama
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person watching family movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | time-travel | family   |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, chef, dressmaker
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the dressmaker is between the chef and the owner of the pony##2
2. the chef is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the dressmaker is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Job   | chef | dressmaker | mechanic |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, badminton, volleyball
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Sport   | skateboarding  | volleyball     | badminton |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | jazz    |

