The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, house, salsa
1. the fan of salsa is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the fan of house is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Sport          | snowboarding | cycling | volleyball  |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | ambient  | house |

