.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-17::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, thai, turkish
City: hamburg, marseilles, edinburgh
1. the american is on the left of the turkish##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4
4. the thai is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Nationality   | american | turkish | thai    |
| City           | marseilles     | edinburgh  | hamburg |

