.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, grey, chestnut
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, jazz
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person who likes yellow is in the middle##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Color         | chestnut | yellow   | grey |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | classical | jazz      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
City: hamburg, london, prague
1. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | soy-milk |
| City   | london   | prague          | hamburg |

